Game information:  


Total War: Rome 2 will provide an opportunity to manage the first world
superpower and command her striking and numerous armies to subdue opponents
political, military or economic means. Game from the creators of the Total
War series combines elements of real-time gameplay and stepping mode.
During the campaign, you can move for move to conquer the land, and enjoy
the battles involving tens of thousands of people under your command in real
time. Heavily modified engine Warscape in Total War: Rome 2 will allow to
consider the exotic cities to the smallest detail, and the new camera will
make it possible to observe the battlefield from any angle.
